Development:

	Magnus has been developed by Alexandre Trilla
	for the IT Projects Unit of the Ministry of
	Education of The Government of Catalonia 
	(The Generalitat de Catalunya).

	Its development platform has been Linkat 2,
	which is the GNU/Linux distribution for
	education promoted by The Government of
	Catalunya.

	Magnus constitutes the Master Thesis of
	its author, who has coursed Engineering in
	Telecommunications in Universitat Ramon
	Llull La Salle in Barcelona.


